    • Method Detail

      • onGarbageCollectionRejection

        <T> void onGarbageCollectionRejection(T rejectedBean)
        Method should be called if a bean get rejected by the Dolphin Platform garbage collection. This means that the bean isn't referenced anymore by another bean and can be removed. Implementations shoudl removePresentationModel the bean from the model / remoting layer. For more information see GarbageCollector
        Type Parameters:
        T - type of the bean.
        Parameters:
        rejectedBean - the rejected bean
